derivation: from G2596 (κατέρχομαι) and G2064 (κατέρχομαι) (including its alternate);
kjv_def: come (down), depart, descend, go down, land
strongs_def: to come (or go) down (literally or figuratively)
outline:
1. to come down, go down
    1. of one who goes from a higher to a lower locality
    2. of those who come to a place by a ship
